quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  36,51,“Ndipo lipenga lidzaimbidwa (loukitsa akufa); iwo adzangozindikira akutuluka m’manda kunka kwa Mbuye wawo uku akuthamanga
  36,52,"“Adzati: “Kalanga ife! Kodi ndani watidzutsa pogona pathu?” (Adzawauza): “Izi ndi zimene adalonjeza (Allah), Wachifundo chambiri ndi zimene adanena atumiki moona.”"
  36,53,“Sipadzakhala (china) koma mkuwe umodzi basi; adzangozindikira iwo onse atabweretsedwa patsogolo Pathu
  36,54,““Ndipo mzimu uliwonse lero suponderezedwa pa chilichonse. Ndipo mulipidwa pa zokhazo munkachita.”
  36,55,“Ndithu anthu aku Jannah (Munda wamtendere) lero akhala wotanganidwa ndi chisangalalo
  36,56,“Iwo ndi akazi awo ali m’mithunzi uku atatsamira mipando (ya mtengo wapamwamba)
  36,57,“M’menemo apeza (mtundu uliwonse) wa zipatso ndiponso apeza chilichonse chimene akuchifuna
  36,58,"““Mtendere (pa iwo)!” Limeneli ndi liwu lochokera kwa Mbuye (wawo), Wachisoni chosatha"
  36,59,"“Ndipo dzipatuleni lero, inu oipa"
  36,60,"“Kodi sindidakulangizeni, E inu ana a Adam kuti musapembedze satana? Ndithu, iye ndi mdani woonekera kwa inu"
  36,61,“Ndikuti ndipembedzeni Ine? Imeneyi ndi njira yolunjika
  36,62,“Ndithu (satana) adasokeretsa anthu ambiri mwa inu. Kodi simumaganizira mwanzeru
  36,63,“Iyi ndi Jahena yomwe mumalonjezedwa
  36,64,"“Iloweni lero, chifukwa cha kunkana kwanu (Allah)"
  36,65,“Lero titseka kukamwa kwawo. Ndipo manja awo atiyankhula ndipo miyendo yawo ichitira umboni pa zomwe amachita
  36,66,"“Ndipo tikadafuna, tikadafafaniza maso awo; ndipo akadakhala akuthamangira njira; koma akadapenya chotani"
  36,67,"“Ndipo tikadafuna, tikadawasintha kukhala ndi maonekedwe a nyama pamalo pawo pomwepo (pamene adali), kotero kuti sakadatha kuyenda (kunka patsogolo) ngakhale kubwerera pambuyo"